OL,3,C'Gifted' teenager died on mental
OL,4,Chealth unit after 'lapses in
OL,5,Cmonitoring'
OL,7,FThere were lapses in the monitoring of
OL,8,Fa 19-year-old woman from Street who
OL,9,Fdied while detained under the Mental
OL,10,FHealth Act, an inquest has heard.
OL,12,FCariss Stone died at Musgrove Park
OL,13,FHospital in August 2019, two days
OL,14,Fafter being found unresponsive with a
OL,15,Fligature round her neck on Holford
OL,16,FWard at Wellsprings Hospital.
OL,18,FShe was being held at the NHS
OL,19,Fpsychiatric intensive care unit in
OL,20,FTaunton under a section.
