OL,3,C'Gifted' teenager died on mental
OL,4,Chealth unit after 'lapses in
OL,5,Cmonitoring'
OL,7,FAn inquest into her death, held before
OL,8,Fa jury of seven women and three men,
OL,9,Fbegan at Wells Town Hall on Tuesday 2
OL,10,FApril.
OL,12,FThe jury heard how the teenager had a
OL,13,Flong history of anorexia, self-harm
OL,14,Fand suicide attempts - sometimes being
OL,15,Fadmitted to emergency departments
OL,16,Fseveral times weekly.
OL,18,FShe had been detained under the Mental
OL,19,FHealth Act six times previously.
