OL,3,C'Gifted' teenager died on mental
OL,4,Chealth unit after 'lapses in
OL,5,Cmonitoring'
OL,7,FAt the time of her death, Cariss was
OL,8,Fjudged a high enough risk to herself
OL,9,Fto require welfare checks every five
OL,10,Fminutes.
OL,12,FNicholas Rheinberg, assistant coroner
OL,13,Ffor Somerset, told the jury that there
OL,14,Fwere lapses in this monitoring regime.
OL,16,FThe jury also heard that Samantha
OL,17,FSands, the Holford staff member
OL,18,Fresponsible for Cariss's observations
OL,19,Fat the time she was found with the
OL,20,Fligature, was medically unfit to
OL,21,Fappear at the inquest.
