OL,3,C'Gifted' teenager died on mental
OL,4,Chealth unit after 'lapses in
OL,5,Cmonitoring'
OL,7,FThe coroner said options to facilitate
OL,8,FMs Sands' evidence were still being
OL,9,Fexamined.
OL,11,FCariss's mother, Gina Schiraldi, told
OL,12,Fthe inquest her daughter was "bright,
OL,13,Fcaring and compassionate".
OL,15,FShe had been part of the Gifted and
OL,16,FTalented Programme at Crispin School
OL,17,Fin Street, before going on to study
OL,18,FHealth and Social Care at Strode
OL,19,FCollege, where she made good friends
OL,20,Fand served as a volunteer police cadet.
