OL,3,C'Gifted' teenager died on mental
OL,4,Chealth unit after 'lapses in
OL,5,Cmonitoring'
OL,7,FShe said Cariss was first hospitalised
OL,8,Ffor anorexia when she was 14 and her
OL,9,Fmental health struggles began to
OL,10,Fescalate. At times, she needed a
OL,11,Ffeeding tube and used a wheelchair.
OL,13,FAndreas Papadopoulos, Cariss's
OL,14,Fpsychiatrist until shortly before her
OL,15,Fdeath, told the inquest it was likely
OL,16,Fthat the teenager had Emotionally
OL,17,FUnstable Personality Disorder.
