OL,3,C'Gifted' teenager died on mental
OL,4,Chealth unit after 'lapses in
OL,5,Cmonitoring'
OL,7,FThe condition may have been caused by
OL,8,Fthe trauma of witnessing domestic
OL,9,Fabuse as a child and could explain her
OL,10,Fbehaviour.
OL,12,FIn March 2019, Cariss was admitted
OL,13,Funder section to St Andrew's Ward, an
OL,14,Facute psychiatric unit in Wells, due
OL,15,Fto more serious acts of self-harm, and
OL,16,Fwas transferred to Holford Ward after
OL,17,Fher condition deteriorated.
