OL,3,C'Gifted' teenager died on mental
OL,4,Chealth unit after 'lapses in
OL,5,Cmonitoring'
OL,7,FThat summer, she was found using a
OL,8,Fligature on 55 occasions. However,
OL,9,Fjust before her death, staff had
OL,10,Freported an improvement in her mental
OL,11,Fhealth.
OL,13,FIn a statement, Cariss's younger
OL,14,Fbrother, Luke Stone, told the inquest
OL,15,Fthat his "gentle-hearted" sister had
OL,16,Fbeen through more mental health
OL,17,Fservices and wards than he could
OL,18,Fremember, but "none seemed to give her
OL,19,Fthe right support".
